 1999-13511999-07-280,  ,  INDUSTRY,  , 
PrecisEnactment of the EXCEPTIONS FOR EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS, LIBRARIES, ARCHIVES AND MUSEUMS REGULATIONS which permit non-profit libraries, archives and museums, or persons acting under their authority, to do anything on behalf of a person that a person may do while he or she is engaged in the research, private study, criticism or review of copyrighted material, effective September 1, 1999.
